author: fmeschbe
msg: FELIX-2231 Ensure components for cannot be loaded twice: Access to the map of loaded components per bundle was not synchronized. In addition, there was a relatively big window between the check whether a bundle's components have been loaded and the actual registration of the loaded components. This has now been closed using a flag set early and replaced with the actual loaded components.
